2.0.name: wordpress/rtpanel
2.0.description: WordPress theme framework with Custom Menu, Header and Background along with Logo, Favicon, Featured Image, Feedburner, Facebook Open Graph, Google Custom Search Integration and more options. Now includes a SAAS based CSS preprocessor and translation support. This theme comes with free technical support by team of 20+ full-time developers.
